                    <p class="section-text" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-weight: 100; font-size: 15.5px; text-align: center;">
                        Since our founding in 2014, we have been driven by the goal of ensuring that no one has to freeze. Our vests offer lifesaving relief from suffering for those who are homeless and provide a meaningful way to serve for volunteers and participants.
