                        <h2>Adam — Vest Recipient</h2>
                        <p style="font-family: sans-serif; font-weight: 100; font-size: 15.5px; text-align: center;">
                            "Before I received the vest, I was struggling to survive the cold nights on the streets. Every day was a battle against the freezing temperatures, and I didn't know how much longer I could hold on. Since receiving the vest, everything changed. I can now keep warm even in the harshest conditions, and it has given me a sense of hope that I didn’t have before. The warmth it provides, especially when I get wet, has saved my life. I feel like I have a fighting chance now."
                        </p>
